Other Sites of Possible Interest

   USGS sources
     * National Water Conditions monthly report and map
     * National Water Information System (NWIS) for historical data.
     * GNIS -- Geographic Names Information System - Give a name, get a
       lat/lon

   Non-USGS sources
     * National Weather Service -- Current Hydrologic Conditions
     * National Weather Service River Forecast Centers and Weather
       Forecast Offices
     * Weather maps (WXP, Purdue University)
     * Recreational Opportunities on Federal Lands

   ----------

   We want your comments! Your email helps us set priorities for further
   development and gain support for these efforts. Please see our feedback
   page. You can also express your views to the USGS Water Resources
   District Chief for your state.

   Webmasters! You can construct persistent links directly to an
   individual station page. Use the format
   http://water.usgs.gov/cgi-bin/realsta.pl?station=xxxxxxxx where
   "xxxxxxxx" is the (usually) 8-digit station identification number.

